<exercise id="fs-idp41306208">
<problem id="fs-idp24323216">
<para id="fs-idp15374976">What is the molecular structure about the nitrogen atom in trimethyl amine and in the trimethyl ammonium ion, (CH<sub>3</sub>)<sub>3</sub>NH<sup>+</sup>? What is the hybridization of the nitrogen atom in trimethyl amine and in the trimethyl ammonium ion?</para>
</problem>
<solution id="fs-idp33005984">
<para id="fs-idp62477392">Trimethyl amine: trigonal pyramidal, <emphasis effect="italics">sp</emphasis><sup>3</sup>; trimethyl ammonium ion: tetrahedral, <emphasis effect="italics">sp</emphasis><sup>3</sup></para>
</solution>
